  "passageParts": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Being a good parent is what every parent would like to be. But defining what it means to be a good parent is undoubtedly very\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, particularly since children respond differently to the same style. of parenting. A calm, rule-following child might respond better to a different sort of parenting than,\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, a younger one.\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, there's another sort of parent that's easier to\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​: a parent. Children of every age benefit from patient parenting. Still,\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, every parent would like to be patient, this is no easy\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, sometimes, parents get exhausted and are unable to maintain a\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nstyle with their kids. I understand this.\n You're only human, and sometimes your kids can\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nyou just a little too far. And then the\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nhappens: You lose your patience and either scream at your kids or say something that was too\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nand does nobody any good.:You wish that you could\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nthe clock and start over. We've all been there.\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, even though it's common, its vital to keep in mind that in a single moment of fatigue, you can say something to your child that you may\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nfor a long time, This may not only do damage to your relationship with your child but also\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nyour child's self-esteem.\n If you consistently lose your\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nwith your kids, then you are modeling a lack of emotional control for your kids. We are all becoming increasingly aware of the\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nof modeling patience for the younger generation. This is a skill that will help them all throughout life. In fact, the ability to maintain emotional control when\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 17
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nby stress is one of the most significant of all life's skills.\n Certainly, it's\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 18
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nto maintain patience at all times with your kids, A more practical goal is to try to be as calm as you can when faced with\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 19
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nsituations involving your children. I can promise you this: As a result of working toward this goal, you and your children will benefit and,\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 20
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nfrom stressful moments fling better physically and emotionally."
    }
  ],
